Package: yadifa
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, debconf, netbase, adduser, lsb-base (>= 3.2-14), libdnscore0 (=${binary:Version}), libdnsdb0 (=${binary:Version}), libdnszone0 (=${binary:Version})
Description: Internet Domain Name Server
 ${Description}
 .
 This package provides the server and related configuration files.

Package: libdnscore0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: DNS Core shared library used by YADIFA
 ${Description}
 .
 This package delivers the dnscore shared library used
 by the YADIFA daemon. It provides basic network and
 DNS query/conversion functions.

Package: libdnsdb0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: DNS DB shared library used by YADIFA
 ${Description}
 .
 This package delivers the dnsdb shared library used
 by the YADIFA daemon. It handles the internal database
 and provides NSEC3 and DNSSEC capabilities.

Package: libdnszone0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: DNS Zone shared library used by YADIFA
 ${Description}
 .
 This package delivers the dnszone shared library used
 by the YADIFA daemon. It handles AXFR and IXFR zone
 transfers.

Package: libyadifa-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libdnscore0 (=${binary:Version}), libdnsdb0 (=${binary:Version}), libdnszone0 (=${binary:Version})
Description: development libraries and header files for YADIFA
 ${Description}
 .
 This package contains the header files and static libraries needed for
 developing applications for YADIFA.

